<p><strong>Damage Resistances</strong> cold, fire, poison</p>

<p><strong>Senses</strong> darkvision 60 ft.</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 1/4 (50 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Charge.</em></strong> If the kow moves at least 20 feet straight toward a target and then hits it with a gore attack on the same turn, the target takes an extra 7 (2d6) piercing damage.</p>

<p><strong><em>Stench.</em></strong> Any creature other than a stench kow that starts its turn within 5 feet of the stench kow must succeed on a DC 26 Constitution saving throw or be poisoned until the start of the creatureâ€™s next turn. On a successful saving throw, the creature is immune to the stench of all stench kows for 1 hour.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Gore.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 7 (1d6+4) piercing damage.</p>

